trans-unit.source: Implements the `ResolveKeySource` task.
Use the `ResolveKeySource` element in your project file to create and execute this task.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av `ResolveKeySource` elementet i prosjektfilen til å opprette og kjøre denne oppgaven.

trans-unit.source: For usage and parameter information, see [ResolveKeySource Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For bruk og parametere informasjon, se [ResolveKeySource oppgaven](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the amount of time, in seconds, to display the count down message.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tiden, i sekunder, for å vise antallet ned meldingen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 15 seconds.
The amount of time, in seconds, to display the count down message.
trans-unit.target: Hvor lang tid, i sekunder, for å vise antallet ned meldingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the amount of time, in seconds, to wait before closing the password prompt dialog.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tiden, i sekunder, skal vente før du lukker dialogboksen passord spør.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 20 seconds.
The amount of time, in seconds, to wait before closing the password prompt dialog.
trans-unit.target: Hvor lang tid i sekunder, skal vente før du lukker dialogboksen passord spør.
